  43,62,"(And let not Satan turn you aside) let not Satan turn you away from the religion of Islam or from belief in the coming of the Hour. (Lo! he is an open enemy for you) whose enmity is quite manifest."
  43,73,"(Therein) in the Garden (for you is fruit) different kinds of fruit (in plenty whence to eat."